{"tid":2300944,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"貓貓今朝係到嘔","createTime":"2020-11-26T02:36:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-26T13:55:02.000Z","uid":198059,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"152b3fa2cbc1d4030d25e0fc7506578a7cd368c7","tid":2300944,"uid":198059,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-26T02:36:45.000Z","msg":"救命 我隻貓今朝無啦啦食完1/4個罐嘔左兩次<br />\n跟住又行入砂盤發出啲作嘔聲但無嘔到<br />\n而家係到行兩行就去飲水<br />\n我見啲人話貓貓好易會嘔<br />\n但我第一次見佢嘔 有啲擔心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n貓貓4個半月大"},{"pid":"5994c90af83336c2b040cac3fd4da4dca188b139","tid":2300944,"uid":177089,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-26T02:37:41.000Z","msg":"見到你就想嘔"},{"pid":"41926a8a6e4ab9de8f923e32116e23463ad27e0b","tid":2300944,"uid":11447,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-26T02:38:36.000Z","msg":"睇醫生啦 上嚟問做乜"},{"pid":"0c5711c382091fbbe80a6fd5a61abb65db236c5e","tid":2300944,"uid":377778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-26T02:40:45.000Z","msg":"會唔會係嘔毛咋？"},{"pid":"aa0ef0eb5c44fb3de375a9722b454e8ec70bd08a","tid":2300944,"uid":43594,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-26T02:43:10.000Z","msg":"貓嘔真係好平常<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你睇吓佢嘔咩出嚟先<br />\n未消化嘅食物？<br />\n如果佢精神無明顯變差 可以再觀察吓<br />\n短時間內再嘔先睇獸醫"},{"pid":"0292e3c756cfde2c15922cbe5916f363130aa01c","tid":2300944,"uid":12302,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-26T02:48:47.000Z","msg":"又搵連登醫生"},{"pid":"863a9384ebd8f9109a6f3e070435874c60f60b0a","tid":2300944,"uid":277186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-26T02:53:35.000Z","msg":"平時有無喂佢食草? 可能係毛球"},{"pid":"d7736343b4d084ac102afa90d6f741125d7280c6","tid":2300944,"uid":198958,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-26T02:54:21.000Z","msg":"嘔毛球"},{"pid":"7531b22e6b767836cc75202e91315a8b475424f7","tid":2300944,"uid":68098,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-26T02:56:45.000Z","msg":"一.有冇小便<br />\n二．有冇成日走入廁所而冇疴尿<br />\n三．有冇狂Lam自己賓周<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如果全中<br />\n馬上去睇醫生<br />\n<br />\n尿道炎<br />\n疴唔到尿"},{"pid":"a855e58349b26cc13ae88f1cdc0420de29feab8c","tid":2300944,"uid":1990,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-26T03:10:18.000Z","msg":"我果隻1個月至幾個月嘔一次都有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c88df7be9f560d7757b8699ef72085be772bcb3e","tid":2300944,"uid":227588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-26T04:40:23.000Z","msg":"有時食得太急都會嘔 ....."},{"pid":"b7201c41a495dda3ce691d3e321734836248436a","tid":2300944,"uid":259071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-26T04:45:02.000Z","msg":"你望下佢會唔會咬到你屋企D野?　<br />\n佢飲水應該係想自己嘔返胃入面既野出黎，最近換毛季，平時有冇比化毛粉佢食？觀察一陣，有問題就帶去睇獸醫啦"},{"pid":"967aa1ecf2888e0b3fcdb1680787bf243093429c","tid":2300944,"uid":120705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-26T05:03:54.000Z","msg":"聽講話貓貓腸胃好敏感<br />\n一有異物吞咗 就會嘔<br />\n<br />\n其實呢個係一個自救機制<br />\n嘔完應該會無乜事<br />\n<br />\n當然 如果持續嘔一日兩日嘅話<br />\n就最好去睇醫生啦<br />\n<br />\n兩三次應該無咩事嘅<br />\n唔使太擔心<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7c674bd6b868b0226ea5de7d4f45f6d58cea10a","tid":2300944,"uid":334170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-26T06:53:59.000Z","msg":"之前試過因為有蟲<br />\n佢有冇杜蟲？"},{"pid":"d412fede9eacd93ace416afe3fd7d7af7aab0449","tid":2300944,"uid":52656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-26T06:57:14.000Z","msg":"有時食飽玩到傻左都會咁<br />\n你睇佢之後食唔食野<br />\n食野又識周圍走咪冇野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4fa58de9cad4ae610123b2009c4c282149fcea22","tid":2300944,"uid":223084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7531b22e6b767836cc75202e91315a8b475424f7","tid":2300944,"uid":68098,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-26T02:56:45.000Z","msg":"一.有冇小便<br />\n二．有冇成日走入廁所而冇疴尿<br />\n三．有冇狂Lam自己賓周<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如果全中<br />\n馬上去睇醫生<br />\n<br />\n尿道炎<br />\n疴唔到尿"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-26T07:10:49.000Z","msg":"如果貓女呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b36c3fcf08c90c644248e9d6df29fea46914b0c2","tid":2300944,"uid":68098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4fa58de9cad4ae610123b2009c4c282149fcea22","tid":2300944,"uid":223084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7531b22e6b767836cc75202e91315a8b475424f7","tid":2300944,"uid":68098,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-26T02:56:45.000Z","msg":"一.有冇小便<br />\n二．有冇成日走入廁所而冇疴尿<br />\n三．有冇狂Lam自己賓周<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如果全中<br />\n馬上去睇醫生<br />\n<br />\n尿道炎<br />\n疴唔到尿"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-26T07:10:49.000Z","msg":"如果貓女呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-26T07:13:56.000Z","msg":"都會有可能尿道炎<br />\n如果超過一日無小便<br />\n會死"},{"pid":"83f61feec6e74aaacd9a993bbdfa44aedf093ad0","tid":2300944,"uid":208334,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-26T13:55:02.000Z","msg":"可能食得太急/ 食完跑來跑去<br />\n如果有精神無軟便可以再觀察下先"}]}